What are you preparing today?

00:00:21.762 --> 00:00:24.437
Ingredients to prepare Papaya Pickle :

00:00:25.444 --> 00:00:30.276
Turmeric powder, Tamarind paste, Salt, Oil

00:00:30.966 --> 00:00:36.078
Mustard powder, Lemon juice, Fenugreek powder, Red Chilli powder.

00:00:56.897 --> 00:00:59.592
Add a pinch of Turmeric powder to the finely chopped Papaya (unripened).

00:01:06.262 --> 00:01:09.298
Add 1 tbsp Red Chilli powder.

00:01:11.140 --> 00:01:13.733
Add 1 tbsp Mustard powder.

00:01:16.301 --> 00:01:18.356
Add 1 tbsp Fenugreek powder.

00:01:19.495 --> 00:01:21.390
Add Salt to taste.

00:01:28.140 --> 00:01:30.244
Add the Tamarind paste.

00:01:34.796 --> 00:01:36.822
Add 2 tsp Lemon juice.

00:01:41.814 --> 00:01:43.852
Add 3 tbsp Oil.

00:01:48.794 --> 00:01:50.878
Mix the ingredients well.

00:02:31.359 --> 00:02:33.593
Soak the pickle for 2 days before serving.

